# Prompted-agentic style prompts (PR 2)
#
# This directory will hold per-spot prompt sequences for the
# pre-prompted-agentic exercise style. PR 1 reserves the slot in the
# schema (paths/<slug>/phases.json `styles["prompted-agentic"].prompts_dir`)
# and the on-disk layout (`prompts/<spot-id>/<n>.md`); PR 2 will populate
# the actual prompts and light up `selectStyle` for this style.
#
# See PR2_BOOTSTRAP.md at the repo root for the full handoff.
